dct_title_s: Survey of Artificial Sand Bar Formed by U.S. Government Dredging and unauthorized occupation on Toms River in Dover Township, Ocean County
dct_description_sm: Map covers area of Toms River and surrounding areas including the C.R.R. of New Jersey Station. Map depicts bulkhead and pierhead lines along Toms River.
